%p.article-title Brilliant! #{@host.first_name.capitalize} has confirmed his service availability for you!
%p.article-content= "Here is all of the contact details we have for #{@host.first_name.capitalize} so you have a record."
%p.article-content The next step is simply for you to handover your pet to the provider at the agreed place and time.
%p.article-content
  Don’t forget to follow the
  = succeed '.' do
    = link_to('House Rules', house_rules_url)
%p.article-content
  Also
  = link_to 'Read Cancellation Policy', cancellation_policy_url
  and
  = succeed '.' do
    = link_to 'Insurance Policy', insurance_policy_url

%p.article-content When you handover your pet, make sure you:
%ul
  %li.article-content Review pick up times & dates
  %li.article-content Review Emergency & contact details
  %li.article-content Transaction for the service as agreed
  %li.article-content Bring food for your pet (owners provide this unless otherwise agreed!)
  %li.article-content Bring a favourite toy or bedding so they feel at home
  %li.article-content Any special instructions such as feeding or walking
%br

%p.article-title Booking Details
%p.article-content
  %i Check In Date
  = ": #{@booking.check_in_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)}"
%p.article-content
  %i Check Out Date
  = ": #{@booking.check_out_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)}"
%p.article-content
  %i Number of stays (24 hour blocks)
  = ": #{@booking.number_of_nights}"
%p.article-content
  %i Rate per night
  = ": $#{@booking.actual_value_figure(:cost_per_night)}"
%p.article-content
  %i Subtotal
  = ": $#{@booking.actual_value_figure(:subtotal)}"
%p.article-content
  %i Credit Card Fee
  = ": $#{@booking.actual_value_figure(:credit_card_fee)}"
%p.article-content
  %strong
    %i Total Amount Paid
  = ": $#{@booking.actual_value_figure(:amount)}"
%br

= render 'shared/brief_pet_details'

%p.article-title Provider details for your records
%p.article-content
  %i Listing
  \:
  = link_to "#{@homestay.title} in #{@homestay.address_suburb}", homestay_url(@homestay)
  - if @homestay.pictures.present?
    %p.article-content= link_to image_tag(@homestay.pictures.first.file.thumb('190x150#').url), homestay_url(@homestay)
%p.article-content
  %i Provider's name
  = ": #{@host.name}"
%p.article-content
  %i Provider's email
  = ": #{@host.email}"
- if @host.phone_number.present?
  %p.article-content
    %i Provider's phone
    = ": #{@host.phone_number}"
- if @host.mobile_number.present?
  %p.article-content
    %i Provider's mobile
    = ": #{@host.mobile_number}"
%p.article-content
  %i Address
  = ": #{@homestay.address_1}"
  = @homestay.address_suburb
  = @homestay.address_city
- if @homestay.address_2.present?
  %p.article-content
    %i Address 2
    = ": #{@homestay.address_2}"
%p.article-content
  %i Professional?
  - if @homestay.is_professional?
    = ': Yes'
  - else
    = ': No'
%p.article-content
  %i Property type
  = ": #{@homestay.property_type_name}"
%p.article-content
  %i Outdoor area
  = ": #{@homestay.outdoor_area_name}"
%p.article-content
  %i Fenced?
  - if @homestay.fenced
    = ': Yes'
  - else
    = ': No'
%p.article-content
  - if @homestay.supervision?
    %i Supervision?
    \:
    = @homestay.pretty_supervision
%p.article-content
  - if @homestay.emergency_preparedness?
    %i Emergency preparedness?
    = ": #{@homestay.pretty_emergency_preparedness}"
%br

%p.article-content Thanks and don’t forget to leave feedback via PetHomeStay on the provider!
%p.article-content The PetHomeStay Team
